## The Digital Descent

The ob3ect compiles itself down through successive substrate layers.

```
seed (frob.py)           Python meta-circular Frobenius check
    тЖУ IMSCRIB
v0.1  (ob3ect-imscriber.py)   Python тАФ Frobenius PASS, Closure: True
    тЖУ AFWD + FSPLIT
v0.2  (.o grammar)       Custom .o grammar тЖТ C native binary
v0.3                     Quine embedding тАФ self.o imscribed in binary
v0.4                     Quine extraction stub activated
v0.5                     Grammar expansion тАФ QUINE opcode
v0.6                     MACRO opcode тАФ language deepening
v0.7                     Entropy pass тАФ ╬ФS тЙИ 0 verified
v0.8                     Full C self-hosting target
v0.9                     Pre-silicon тАФ final C generation
    тЖУ AREV + FFUSE
v0.10 (ob3ect-v0.10.iso) Bare-metal x86 bootloader ISO
```

The descent is a directed path in Prog/~. Each edge is an IMASM morphism.
The final ISO boots and prints the Frobenius identity from bare metal.

