## Structural Typing (IG Coordinates)

Every ob3ect is assigned a 12-primitive coordinate in the Imscribing Grammar lattice
(17,280,000 structural types). The coordinate is assigned during instantiation and
stored in `artifact.structural_type`.

```
Primitive  Symbol  Dimension
тФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФА
├Р          ЁРСж       Dimensionality: imscriptive (self-referential loop)
├Ю          ЁРС╕       Topology: closure (no boundary leakage)
┼Ш          ЁРС╛       Relational mode: bidirectional (parse тЖФ unparse)
╬ж          ЁРС╣       Parity: Frobenius-special (╬╝тИШ╬┤ = id enforced)
╞Т          ЁРСР       Fidelity: quantum (coherent state preserved)
├З          ЁРСз       Kinetics: slow/near-equilibrium (╬ФS тЙИ 0)
╬У          ЁРС▓       Scope: maximal (all programs in Prog/~)
╔в          ЁРСа       Interaction: sequential (THINKтЖТACTтЖТOBSERVE)
╧Ж╠В          тКЩ        Criticality: critical (self-modeling gate open)
─ж          ЁРСл       Chirality: two-step memory (parse remembers unparse)
╬г          ЁРС│       Stoichiometry: many heterogeneous (full tower)
╬й          ЁРСн       Winding: integer (topologically protected loop)
```

Ouroboricity tier **O_тИЮ** is assigned when ╧Ж╠В=тКЩ (criticality=critical) and
╬ж=ЁРС╣ (Frobenius-special) are both active and the winding ╬й=ЁРСн is integer.

